                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Russell</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Caracas</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-02-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 1, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Russell reports that the Venezuelan Government wishes to know if the
                    American consuls in Paris, Marseilles, Bordeaux, etc., can take charge of the
                    archives of the Venezuelan consulates in said towns.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
